queryResponse.sql:
-- raw sql results do not include filled-in values for 'marts_shipments.finance_record_date_month'


SELECT * FROM (
SELECT *, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY z___min_rank) as z___pivot_row_rank, RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY z__pivot_col_rank ORDER BY z___min_rank) as z__pivot_col_ordering, CASE WHEN z___min_rank = z___rank THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS z__is_highest_ranked_cell FROM (
SELECT *, MIN(z___rank) OVER (PARTITION BY "marts_shipments.shipper_name","marts_shipments.shipper_rank") as z___min_rank FROM (
SELECT *, RANK() OVER (ORDER BY "marts_shipments.shipper_rank" ASC, z__pivot_col_rank, "marts_shipments.shipper_name") AS z___rank FROM (
SELECT *, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY CASE WHEN "marts_shipments.finance_record_date_month" IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END, "marts_shipments.finance_record_date_month") AS z__pivot_col_rank FROM (
SELECT
    (TO_CHAR(DATE_TRUNC('month', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(marts_shipments."FINANCE_RECORD_DATE"  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))), 'YYYY-MM')) AS "marts_shipments.finance_record_date_month",
    marts_shipments."SHIPPER_NAME"  AS "marts_shipments.shipper_name",
    marts_shipments.rank AS "marts_shipments.shipper_rank",
    COALESCE(SUM(marts_shipments."MARGIN" ), 0) AS "marts_shipments.sum_margin",
        COALESCE(SUM(marts_shipments."MARGIN" ), 0) / nullif(COALESCE(SUM(marts_shipments."STARK_REVENUE"  ), 0), 0) AS "marts_shipments.total_margin_percent_average",
    COALESCE(SUM(marts_shipments."STARK_REVENUE"  ), 0) AS "marts_shipments.sum_revenue",
    COALESCE(SUM(marts_shipments."SUM_ACCESSORIAL_MARGIN" ), 0) AS "marts_shipments.sum_accessorial_margin"
FROM edw_prod.shipments.marts_shipments  AS marts_shipments
WHERE ((( marts_shipments."FINANCE_RECORD_DATE"  ) >= ((CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(DATEADD('month', -5, DATE_TRUNC('month', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))) AND ( marts_shipments."FINANCE_RECORD_DATE"  ) < ((CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(DATEADD('month', 6, DATEADD('month', -5, DATE_TRUNC('month', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))))) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))))
GROUP BY
    (DATE_TRUNC('month', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(marts_shipments."FINANCE_RECORD_DATE"  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))),
    2,
    3) ww
) bb WHERE z__pivot_col_rank <= 16384
) aa
) xx
) zz
 WHERE (z__pivot_col_rank <= 50 OR z__is_highest_ranked_cell = 1) AND (z___pivot_row_rank <= 20 OR z__pivot_col_ordering = 1) ORDER BY z___pivot_row_rank

-- sql for creating the pivot row totals
SELECT
    marts_shipments."SHIPPER_NAME"  AS "marts_shipments.shipper_name",
    marts_shipments.rank AS "marts_shipments.shipper_rank",
    COALESCE(SUM(marts_shipments."MARGIN" ), 0) AS "marts_shipments.sum_margin",
        COALESCE(SUM(marts_shipments."MARGIN" ), 0) / nullif(COALESCE(SUM(marts_shipments."STARK_REVENUE"  ), 0), 0) AS "marts_shipments.total_margin_percent_average",
    COALESCE(SUM(marts_shipments."STARK_REVENUE"  ), 0) AS "marts_shipments.sum_revenue",
    COALESCE(SUM(marts_shipments."SUM_ACCESSORIAL_MARGIN" ), 0) AS "marts_shipments.sum_accessorial_margin"
FROM edw_prod.shipments.marts_shipments  AS marts_shipments
WHERE ((( marts_shipments."FINANCE_RECORD_DATE"  ) >= ((CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(DATEADD('month', -5, DATE_TRUNC('month', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))) AND ( marts_shipments."FINANCE_RECORD_DATE"  ) < ((CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(DATEADD('month', 6, DATEADD('month', -5, DATE_TRUNC('month', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))))) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))))
GROUP BY
    1,
    2
ORDER BY
    2
FETCH NEXT 30000 ROWS ONLY

SELECT *, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY z___min_rank) as z___pivot_row_rank, RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY z__pivot_col_rank ORDER BY z___min_rank) as z__pivot_col_ordering, CASE WHEN z___min_rank = z___rank THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS z__is_highest_ranked_cell FROM (

SELECT *, RANK() OVER (ORDER BY "marts_shipments.shipper_rank" ASC, z__pivot_col_rank, "marts_shipments.shipper_name") AS z___rank FROM (
SELECT *, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY CASE WHEN "marts_shipments.finance_record_date_month" IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END, "marts_shipments.finance_record_date_month") AS z__pivot_col_rank FROM (
SELECT
    (TO_CHAR(DATE_TRUNC('month', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(marts_shipments."FINANCE_RECORD_DATE"  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))), 'YYYY-MM')) AS "marts_shipments.finance_record_date_month",
    marts_shipments."SHIPPER_NAME"  AS "marts_shipments.shipper_name",
    marts_shipments.rank AS "marts_shipments.shipper_rank",
    COALESCE(SUM(marts_shipments."MARGIN" ), 0) AS "marts_shipments.sum_margin",
        COALESCE(SUM(marts_shipments."MARGIN" ), 0) / nullif(COALESCE(SUM(marts_shipments."STARK_REVENUE"  ), 0), 0) AS "marts_shipments.total_margin_percent_average",
    COALESCE(SUM(marts_shipments."STARK_REVENUE"  ), 0) AS "marts_shipments.sum_revenue",
    COALESCE(SUM(marts_shipments."SUM_ACCESSORIAL_MARGIN" ), 0) AS "marts_shipments.sum_accessorial_margin"
FROM edw_prod.shipments.marts_shipments  AS marts_shipments
WHERE ((( marts_shipments."FINANCE_RECORD_DATE"  ) >= ((CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(DATEADD('month', -5, DATE_TRUNC('month', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))) AND ( marts_shipments."FINANCE_RECORD_DATE"  ) < ((CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(DATEADD('month', 6, DATEADD('month', -5, DATE_TRUNC('month', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))))) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))))
GROUP BY
    (DATE_TRUNC('month', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(marts_shipments."FINANCE_RECORD_DATE"  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))),
    2,
    3) ww
) bb WHERE z__pivot_col_rank <= 16384
) aa
) xx
) zz
 WHERE (z__pivot_col_rank <= 50 OR z__is_highest_ranked_cell = 1) AND (z___pivot_row_rank <= 20 OR z__pivot_col_ordering = 1) ORDER BY z___pivot_row_rank
